---
title: Honey Roasted Carrot Farro & Kale Salad with Cranberries, Walnuts & Creamy Herb Dressing
description: Farro, a variety of hulled wheat, is praised for its chewy texture and nutty flavor. To make this salad really shine, we paired the tasty ancient grain with spicy glazed honey roasted carrots and walnuts, sweet-tart marinated cranberries, lemony dressing, fresh kale, and a creamy herb dressing. This dinner is so good, it’s almost not farro to the other grain bowls in the world.
image: https://img.hellofresh.com/f_auto,fl_lossy,h_640,q_auto,w_1200/hellofresh_s3/image/honey-roasted-carrot-farro-kale-salad-63c53217.jpg
